metadata.name: Head Space #1
metadata.description: Head Spaces is a generative art project comprised of over 200 hand-drawn illustrations. The collection of 3000 pieces lives on the Ethereum blockchain, each as an individual ERC721 token. The project showcases intricate lines, a complex colour palette, and a repeating, relatable theme - mental health. In a way that often words cannot represent, the artwork aims to depict different moods, emotions, and memories. Each scene opens a window for unique interpretation and connection.
